{
  "info": {
    "name": "ae3/auth-security",
    "description": "Postman Collection do pacote ae3/auth-security — MFA + senha forte + bloqueio de conta. ESQUELETO INICIAL — o desenvolvedor preenche bodies reais, test scripts de captura e exemplos de resposta durante a implementação. Referência: docs/postman/README.md e CONTINUIDADE.md §13 do snapshot de planejamento.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_postman_id": "ae3-auth-security-v01-skeleton"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{access_token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://127.0.0.1:8000" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0. Sandbox auth (fora do pacote)",
      "description": "Rotas de autenticação da app sandbox que envolvem o pacote. NÃO fazem parte do pacote — são usadas para obter o access_token Sanctum antes de chamar as rotas do pacote.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /login (sandbox)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["login"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"tl@teste.local\",\n  \"password\": \"TestForte!1\"\n}" },
            "description": "Login Sanctum da app sandbox. O dev deve adicionar test script que captura o token em {{access_token}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /logout (sandbox)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/logout", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["logout"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1. Login com MFA",
      "description": "Fluxo da segunda etapa após o login Sanctum. Referência: CONTINUIDADE §13.1 e §13.5.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /mfa/factors/{factor_id}/challenge",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/factors/{{factor_id}}/challenge",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "factors", "{{factor_id}}", "challenge"]
            },
            "description": "Inicia o desafio do segundo fator. Resposta depende do type do fator: email/sms → envia OTP e devolve masked_identifier; authenticator_app/recovery_code → não envia, devolve apenas instruction. Test script: capturar challenge_id."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /mfa/verify",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/verify",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "verify"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"challenge_id\": \"{{challenge_id}}\",\n  \"code\": \"123456\"\n}" },
            "description": "Valida o código do segundo fator. Sucesso devolve mfa_session_token. Test script: capturar em {{mfa_session_token}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /mfa/challenges/{challenge_id}/resend",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/challenges/{{challenge_id}}/resend",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "challenges", "{{challenge_id}}", "resend"]
            },
            "description": "Reenvia OTP. Só faz sentido para email/sms. TOTP/recovery_code → 400 RESEND_NOT_ALLOWED. Limite RN-SEG09: 3 reenvios @ 30s."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /mfa/factors/alternatives",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/factors/alternatives",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "factors", "alternatives"]
            },
            "description": "Caminho alternativo (CA-SEG13) — lista outros fatores ativos quando o usuário aciona 'Não tenho mais acesso a este canal'."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Gestão de fatores",
      "description": "CRUD de fatores. Referência: CONTINUIDADE §13.2 e §13.6.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /mfa/factors",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/factors",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "factors"]
            },
            "description": "Lista fatores ativos do usuário. Resource exibe masked_identifier — nunca o valor completo."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /mfa/factors (email)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/factors",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "factors"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"type\": \"email\",\n  \"identifier\": \"tl@teste.local\",\n  \"name\": \"Meu e-mail\"\n}" },
            "description": "Cadastra fator de e-mail. Envia OTP de confirmação para o identifier informado. Test script: capturar factor_id_pending e enrollment_challenge_id."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /mfa/factors (sms)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/factors",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "factors"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"type\": \"sms\",\n  \"identifier\": \"+5511999999999\",\n  \"name\": \"Meu celular\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /mfa/factors (authenticator_app)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/factors",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "factors"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"type\": \"authenticator_app\",\n  \"name\": \"iPhone do trabalho\"\n}" },
            "description": "Cadastra fator TOTP. Resposta inclui qr_code_svg (base64) e secret legível — uma única vez. O usuário lê com app verificador e confirma com o primeiro código."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /mfa/factors/{factor_id_pending}/confirm",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/factors/{{factor_id_pending}}/confirm",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "factors", "{{factor_id_pending}}", "confirm"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"enrollment_challenge_id\": \"{{enrollment_challenge_id}}\",\n  \"code\": \"123456\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "DELETE /mfa/factors/{factor_id}",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/factors/{{factor_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "factors", "{{factor_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Remove fator. Bloqueia com 409 LAST_FACTOR_REQUIRED se for o último e o perfil exigir (RN-SEG11)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Códigos de recuperação",
      "description": "CONTINUIDADE §13.3.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /mfa/recovery-codes",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/recovery-codes",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "recovery-codes"]
            },
            "description": "Metadados apenas — generation_id, total, remaining, last_generated_at. Nunca os códigos."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /mfa/recovery-codes (primeira geração)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/recovery-codes",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "recovery-codes"]
            },
            "description": "Primeira geração — sem body. Devolve os 8 códigos uma única vez."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /mfa/recovery-codes (regeneração)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/recovery-codes",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "recovery-codes"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"confirm_invalidation\": true\n}" },
            "description": "Regenera a lista. Sem confirm_invalidation → 409 INVALIDATION_REQUIRED."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Recuperação assistida",
      "description": "CONTINUIDADE §13.4 + RN-SEG12/13/14.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /mfa/assisted-recoveries (criar)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/assisted-recoveries",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "assisted-recoveries"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"target_user_id\": 123,\n  \"reason_category\": \"device_lost\",\n  \"reason_text\": null\n}" },
            "description": "Admin da organização (ou admin do sistema, se target é admin da org) inicia o pedido. Motivo da lista controlada (RN-SEG12)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /mfa/assisted-recoveries/{id}/release",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/assisted-recoveries/{{recovery_id}}/release",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "assisted-recoveries", "{{recovery_id}}", "release"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"admin_reverification_code\": \"123456\"\n}" },
            "description": "Após reverificação reforçada do admin (TEC-10), gera token único e dispara link ao usuário."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /mfa/assisted-recoveries/complete",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/assisted-recoveries/complete",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "assisted-recoveries", "complete"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"<token-do-link-unico>\"\n}" },
            "description": "Chamada pelo usuário recuperado. Abre sessão temporária com must_register_factor=true (paga TEC-11)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /mfa/assisted-recoveries/{id}/refuse",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/mfa/assisted-recoveries/{{recovery_id}}/refuse",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "mfa", "assisted-recoveries", "{{recovery_id}}", "refuse"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"reason_text\": \"Identidade não confirmada — usuário não soube responder as perguntas de verificação.\"\n}" }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "5. Política da organização",
      "description": "CONTINUIDADE §13.7 + RN-SEG01.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /organization-policies",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/organization-policies?tenant_id=1",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "organization-policies"],
              "query": [{ "key": "tenant_id", "value": "1" }]
            },
            "description": "Matriz perfil × contexto. Cada célula tem source: policy | floor | inherited."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "PUT /organization-policies",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/organization-policies",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "organization-policies"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"tenant_id\": 1,\n  \"entries\": [\n    { \"role\": \"administrator\", \"context\": \"web_admin\", \"requires_mfa\": true },\n    { \"role\": \"administrator\", \"context\": \"citizen\", \"requires_mfa\": false },\n    { \"role\": \"fiscal\", \"context\": \"web_admin\", \"requires_mfa\": true }\n  ]\n}" },
            "description": "Configurar a política. Tentativa de afrouxar abaixo do piso → 422 BELOW_FLOOR com conflicts apontados."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "6. Senha",
      "description": "CONTINUIDADE §13.8 + TEC-03.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth-security/password",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth-security", "password"]
            },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"current_password\": \"TestForte!1\",\n  \"new_password\": \"NovaForte!2\",\n  \"new_password_confirmation\": \"NovaForte!2\"\n}" },
            "description": "Altera senha. Violação de política → 422 WEAK_PASSWORD com violations: [min_length | classes_required | in_history | blacklisted]."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
